# ğŸ’³ Credit Card Fraud Detection System

A Machine Learning project focused on detecting fraudulent credit card transactions using classification algorithms and advanced data preprocessing techniques.

---

## ğŸ“Œ Problem Overview

Credit card fraud causes significant financial losses worldwide.  
The challenge lies in detecting fraudulent transactions from highly imbalanced datasets where fraud cases represent only a small percentage of total transactions.

This project builds a classification model to accurately identify fraudulent transactions while minimizing false negatives.

---

## ğŸ“Š Dataset Information

- Highly imbalanced dataset
- Contains anonymized transaction features
- Target variable:
