## ğŸ“ˆ Evaluation Metrics

Since fraud detection is a sensitive problem, the following metrics were used:

- Precision  
- Recall  
- F1-Score  
- Confusion Matrix  

Special focus was placed on **Recall**, to reduce false negatives.

